Package: causalwiz
Type: Package
Title: Tools for causal inference analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Carmine Minichini
Maintainer: Carmine Minichini <carmine.mnc@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for causal inference analysis in R. 
    Provides functions for estimating treatment effects using various statistical
    methods, features built-in plotting functions and utilities designed for
    causal inference workflows in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
